snippet.title: DREAMER'S WEB GAMEPLAY
snippet.description:
GAMEPLAY VIDEO OF FINNIGAN PRODUCTIONS FIRST RPG VIDEO GAME "DREAMER'S WEB". Please watch, enjoy and comment.  We are currently in the development stage and are hoping to become greenlit by Steam soon! Please follow our concept page on Steam at: 
http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=896169570

www.finniganproductions.com
